'''National Organization of Bessarabia "Arcaşii lui Ştefan"''' ([[Romanian language|Romanian]]:''Organizaţia Naţională din Basarabia "Arcaşii lui Ştefan"'') was one of the organized anti-[[Soviet Union|Soviet]] groups in [[Bessarabia]].
== Activity == National Organization of Bessarabia was formed in 1945, on the territory of the former [[Soroca County (Romania)|Soroca County]] by teachers [[Vasile Bătrânac]], [[Victor Solovei]], [[Nicolae Prăjină]], [[Teodosie Guzun]], [[Anton Romaşcan]] a student, [[Nichita Brumă]].
