An '''emergency notification app''' is a [[Application software|software application]] designed to broadcast emergency notifications to one or multiple groups of contacts via various delivery methods. It is built to run on [[mobile device]]s such as [[smartphone]]s and [[tablet computer]]s. An emergency notification app may be part of a wider [[emergency notification system]] or it may be provided as an alternative to such a system.

